ygData.subject: Re: Giant fire beetle?
ygData.msgSnippet: I don t think Giant Fire Beetles exist. Someone in my guild asked that and I ve never seen em. I ve seen Fire Beetles, and Giant Beetles, but not Giant Fire
ygData.messageBody:
I don't think Giant Fire Beetles exist. Someone in my guild asked that and
I've never seen em. I've seen Fire Beetles, and Giant Beetles, but not Giant
Fire Beetles. If they do exist, it's on one of the outlying islands, not on
the main continent (I've been everywhere but Cazith-Thule and the
"evil-race" towns).
